snippet.title: Luminous Avenger iX - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready for the apeX of 2D action!

Announced at BitSummit 2018 in Kyoto, Japan, the next game in the Azure Striker Gunvolt series, "Gunvolt Chronicles: Luminous Avenger iX", is now in development! 

Title: Gunvolt Chronicles: Luminous Avenger iX
Genre: 2D Action
No. of Players: 1 Player
Release Date: TBD
System: Nintendo Switch
Price: TBD
